data.description: Gorgeous updated brick home nestled in sought-after Brookhaven! This home's elegant interior finishes and beautiful open floor plan are sure to capture your heart. This fantastic property features a spacious remodeled chef's kitchen, gleaming hardwood floors, finished terrace level, and soaring ceilings. Natural light brightens and adorns this wonderful home through the open skylights. The eat-in kitchen welcomes rich 42" cabinets, gleaming quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances. The entry of the home opens to the vaulted ceiling great room, ideal for entertaining. Your gatherings will surely extend out to the spacious deck and fenced backyard. Upstairs you will immediately notice the huge extra bedroom, which could also serve as an additional living space or an excellent office. All the guest bedrooms are large and a full remodeled guest bathroom completes this beautiful home. A full finished terrace level is also an amazing feature of this home and allows you the opportunity to have three full levels of living space; utilize the space for a home gym, office, and more! The master suite features a spacious master bathroom complete with a separate garden tub and shower. This home is situated in a highly desirable location - just seconds from I-85, GA-400, I-285, Buford Hwy & Lenox Rd for fast access to any part of Atlanta - with close proximity to Buckheads premier shopping, Atlanta's best restaurants, dozens of amazing parks and excellent schools. Come visit this gem before it's gone!
